0 HAILCORPSE HC~

Syntax:
	hailcorpse
	hc

The Gods of Xania bestowed the powers of Necromantic Restoration upon
several Iscarian High Clerics long ago. Today, traces of these powers remain
in all citizens of Xania in the guise of a divine skill known
as hailcorpse.

In the unfortunate event of being slain, travel to a location very
near to where your corpse lies. Then incant the Sacred Verses of
Necrosis and your corpse will be summoned. Use caution as incanting
the Sacred Verses of Necrosis can take some time, leaving you exposed
to hazards. You can hail your corpse if it has become trapped in a
particularly dangerous place.
